11/10/2010
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- US Secretary of State Hillary Clinton is arriving late on Monday (October 11th) in Sarajevo, the first leg of her Balkan tour. Clinton will meet with political leaders and will open the new US Embassy in the city. She is expected to urge BiH to continue reforms and to reaffirm US readiness to assist the country in its Euro-Atlantic bid. Clinton travels next to Belgrade and Pristina. (Srna, sarajevo-x.com, BHRT - 10/10/10)
